pageTitle: Astros County: Your Neighborhood Astros Blog & Grill: Matchup for G19 - Brewers at Astros
textBeforeTable: Last two starts: Russ Ortiz will attempt to build on the last four innings of his last outing and string some innings together where he isn't pushing a pitch count limit by the end of the third inning. This will be his third start of the season. Russ Ortiz The Astros end their 10-game homestand in which they were thoroughly unimpressive. Losing a series to the Reds, winning one - surprisingly - against the Dodgers, and losing this series against the Brewers. Matchup for G19 - Brewers at Astros Sunday, April 26, 2009
